nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE A LITTLE WEAKER AS IT CONTINUES EAST-SOUTHEASTWARD...
summary: ...OCTAVE A LITTLE WEAKER AS IT CONTINUES EAST-SOUTHEASTWARD... As of 2:00 PM PDT Tue Oct 07 the center of Octave was located near 15.3, -118.8 with movement ESE at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 45 mph.
